<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- Include the header partial -->
    <%- include ('partials/header.ejs') %>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> NZ COLLEGE OF EDUCATION AUCKLAND</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="top-bar">
            <p>Faculty changes have taken effect from 1 January. <a href="/findmore">Find out more</a></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Include the header navbar -->
        <%- include ('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>

        <div class="university-header">
            <h1> NZ COLLEGE OF EDUCATION AUCKLAND</h1>
            <p>Get set for your future with a qualification. You’ll gain the skills you need to seamlessly transition from study to industry. Become work-ready, capable and confident. </p>
            <img style="width: 100%; height: 450px;" src="https://www.auckland.ac.nz/content/auckland/en/jcr:content/banner/imageMD.img.768.medium.jpg/1740710089229.jpg" alt="Students walking together outside">
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="College">
        <div class="uoa">
            <div class="content">
                <h1 role="heading" aria-level="1">Student-hub</h1>
                <p>Drop in to a Student Hub near you for advice on any aspect of your studies and life at University.</p>
                <a href="/findmore" class="btn-btn--white">Find out more</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <img style="height: 230px; position: inherit; right: 750px; bottom: 30px" src="./public/css/images/image10.jpg" alt="Students studying together">
        <p style="position: inherit; left: -200px; bottom: 220px">
            Our prestigious college is ranked among the top institutions globally, offering exceptional education and vibrant campus life. The <strong>Student Hub</strong> provides personalized support, guiding students in academics, career advice, and well-being. 
            With expert staff and modern resources, we empower students to achieve success in every aspect of their journey.
        </p>
    </div>

<main>
    <section class="explore-options">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Explore Your Options</h2>
            <p>Ask any of our graduates—our 'learn by doing' approach makes for a memorable and valuable study experience. Our skilled and motivated graduates are highly sought-after!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="./public/css/images/image10.jpg" alt="Students studying together">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="qualifications">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="./public/css/images/image12.jpg" alt="Students in a classroom">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>150+ Qualifications and Courses</h2>
            <p>Whether you want to work indoors or out, in a creative or technical field, or something in-between, we have a qualification for you. Browse our programmes or let a career advisor help you figure out your next big step.</p>
            <a href="/courses" class="cta-button">Choose a Course</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flexible-study">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Flexible Study Options</h2>
            <p>As well as our on-campus locations, we also offer other forms of learning so you can have a choice about what, when, where, and how you learn!</p>
            <a href="/study-options" class="cta-button">See Study Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="./public/css/images/image8.jpg" alt="Student studying online">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="free-fees">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="./public/css/images/image9.jpg" alt="Student receiving a scholarship">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Free Fees & Scholarships</h2>
            <p>Your study should give you the best chance to achieve what you want in life. Cost should not be a barrier. Apply for one of our many scholarships or take advantage of government schemes like Fees Free. In some cases, your study could be completely free!</p>
            <a href="/funding" class="cta-button">Find Funding</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 NZ COLLEGE OF EDUCATION AUCKLAND</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
